				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\dot{m}_{\text{ew}}$$\end{document}) obtained from PVT-FPC SS-SS is 3.85 kg for three PVT-FPC, which is lesser that the yield obtained from the proposed system [case (I)], i.e., 32.46 kg for the month of February.Table 3
